502d8a8a96f7e31f7a96b20298ad90c3d2e1d","tid":1049562,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"樓主話<br />\n<code>公司即將轉用其他ERP 所以要重新整理Custome Code</code><br />\n點睇都係做完一次就算，要求咁多做咩？<br />\n無論vlookup, match 定 python，最後都會比ERP代替<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:08:13.000Z","msg":"問題係樓主一開始已經用緊match<br />\n正常人應該係base on 樓主個問題同佢講點改<br />\n下面個個反射式咁vlookup做乜鳩先？"},{"pid":"6de8133929a0ecc022aa1ed3110a7489ba072a68","tid":1049562,"uid":44823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:52:57.000Z","msg":"轉SAP?"},{"pid":"6899ac11c3599662586f4e185b50117a1e324660","tid":1049562,"uid":184374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:05:45.000Z","msg":"起兩邊excel既e1格打「=a1&amp;b1」再複製條式落到底。<br />\n再vlookup兩邊excel既e column，出到result就係a欄+b欄一樣既資料同時兩邊excel都有<br />\n<br />\n利伸：希望無理解錯你想問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108170e489ed0a5d54a88fa14fd41b25acc8be8c","tid":1049562,"uid":114720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbabf5dccfbb956dfd6a603fe24f726b54dd3854","tid":1049562,"uid":33373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T11:07:12.000Z","msg":"公司即將轉用其他ERP 所以要重新整理Custome Code ,我手上有2份 Excel 約8500行<br />\n總部(HQ.xlsx)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FagmbeZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFagmbeZ.png&h=82b7a24a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 分部(BR.xlsx)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wKKyMOC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwKKyMOC.png&h=f426710b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家我HQ.xlsx  第三  、四行對 BR第三 、四<br />\n<br />\n=IF(ISNUMBER(MATCH($A2'[BR.xlsx]Company'!$A:$A,0)),&quot;o&quot;,&quot;x&quot;)<br />\n=IF(ISNUMBER(MATCH($B2'[BR.xlsx]Company'!$B:$B,0)),&quot;o&quot;,&quot;x&quot;)<br />\n<br />\n BR第三 、四對HQ.xlsx  第三  、四行<br />\n=IF(ISNUMBER(MATCH($A2'[HQ.xlsx]Company'!$A:$A,0)),&quot;o&quot;,&quot;x&quot;)<br />\n=IF(ISNUMBER(MATCH($B2'[HQ.xlsx]Company'!$B:$B,0)),&quot;o&quot;,&quot;x&quot;)<br />\n<br />\n因為有部分A行 B行係一樣  所以我Short 第1、2 行o 兩分文件會有 conflict<br />\n<br />\n有咩方法對兩分文件 第1、2 行 (公司名稱有重復)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:11:15.000Z","msg":"最好唔好將result 寫埋同一張sheet.<br />\nresult 最好寫番落去另一張worksheet 度再自己人肉check 番邊個唔compare"},{"pid":"a2b535784b79f867ce9905eed5d1376c0584118e","tid":1049562,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:51:56.000Z","msg":"正常都係分部跟總部既code<br />\n正路都係拎分部個表去比較總部錯左乜<br />\n<br />\n點解你要兩邊比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n媽好亂呀"},{"pid":"b6fafd7347220578de7245cb59bb86a064f63721","tid":1049562,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T09:45:15.000Z","msg":"vba<br />\narray + dictionary<br />\n1秒都唔使搞掂"}]}